Executed `cargo test --workspace`.

Implemented shared engine-facing publication in `crates/transit-core/src/engine.rs`:
- `LocalEngine::publish_rolled_segments` publishes only rolled immutable segments
- publication reads local segment bytes, validates their checksum, and writes them through the `object_store` crate
- published segment descriptors retain the local path while adding an object-store location

The `engine::tests::publishes_rolled_segments_to_object_store_via_shared_engine_code` test verifies that a rolled segment is uploaded and addressable from the object store.
